# API keys (Groq, Deepgram) are entered in-app during onboarding and can be
# rotated any time in Settings — they are not read from the environment.

# Optional: build-time secret used to encrypt stored API keys at rest.
# Export this in the build/run environment (it is read via option_env!/env,
# not from this file). If unset, a built-in fallback secret is used.
#   VOQUILL_API_KEY_SECRET="<random 32+ char string>"
